  <brief_title>CT Perfusion Changes in GI Cancer During Adenosine Vasodilation Test</brief_title>
  <official_title>Abdominal Tissue Perfusion Changes in Esophageal and Gastric Cancer During Adenosine Vasodilation Measured With Computed Tomography (CT) Perfusion</official_title>
